Description:
Create a basic inventory management system that allows users to add, view, update, and delete items from an inventory database. The application will have a command-line interface (CLI) for interacting with the database.

Features:

Add new items to the inventory.
View existing items in the inventory.
Update details of existing items.
Delete items from the inventory.
Tools and Technologies:

MySQL: Database management system
Python: Programming language for application logic
PyMySQL: Python library for connecting to MySQL database
Git: Version control system
GitHub: Hosting platform for sharing and collaborating on code
